557
00:44:53,650 --> 00:44:54,640
Manalangin, maghintay sandali.

558
00:44:55,060 --> 00:44:56,080
Tiya Bud at Tiya Euang,

559
00:44:56,650 --> 00:44:58,600
Kasama ko si Lady Varna buong hapon.

560
00:44:59,270 --> 00:45:00,520
Wala akong alam.

