570
00:45:17,990 --> 00:45:18,720
Hindi, hindi ako ganoon.

571
00:45:19,720 --> 00:45:20,730
Sabi ng aking katulong,

572
00:45:20,750 --> 00:45:23,280
ang taong ito ay may malubhang sugat
