573
00:45:24,030 --> 00:45:25,640
Sino itong kaibigan mo?

574
00:45:28,710 --> 00:45:30,840
Isang matinding sugat sa kaliwang braso.

575
00:45:36,430 --> 00:45:40,280
♫Wat Bot, oh, ang lumang templo,♫

576
